{"tid":2113753,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"依加係香港疫情最嚴峻嘅時刻！唔好唔記得....","createTime":"2020-07-18T10:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T15:24:38.000Z","uid":322642,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f73115025b53f7de5ea266db8fb9438185dfe2","tid":2113753,"uid":322642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">唔好唔記得防疫！<br />\n唔好唔記得正苦所作所為！</span><br />\n<br />\n為配合粤港澳三地檢，正苦放寛強制檢疫及隔離要求！<br />\n六月開始，憑有效健康證明，可自由前往三地，進入目的地及返港後，毋須隔離14日！<br />\n第一日驗完冇事，之後十三日中咗招係冇人知！每日有幾千個往返兩地嘅港商/運輸人員/國安/跨區學童！<br />\n<br />\n六月仲要割免埋世界各地入境船員強制檢疫及14日隔離！<br />\n<br />\n室內傳播率高！竟將室內人數限聚令取消，但就維持禁止喺公眾場所進行羣組聚集！<br />\n<br />\n起勢推送中「健康碼」！想豁免往來三地檢疫要求，方便粵港澳大灣區民眾跨境往來！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">文宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xpnc1RM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxpnc1RM.jpg&h=57247dca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正苦係奶共行先定香港市民安全行先，<br />\n唔洗多講，回顧下佢哋金句！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8n3PjUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8n3PjUU.jpg&h=c1eb6c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMJfZUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMJfZUY.jpg&h=4ada52f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">希望大家有返最開初嘅防疫警覺意識！繼續監察正苦！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb14a23abba09f1cf54d36f8e1fcf334cec024f","tid":2113753,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"武肺測試慢慢由支那化驗公司主導 香港疫情會更唔明確<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2113701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2113701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dcf9386fbc1ce9da1a003039927cac21c6491d6d","